Package: cookcountyil
Title: Cook County, IL Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for Cook County, IL Socrata Open Data portal.
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for property, medical examiner,
    procurement, payroll, and other county datasets.
